<div class="header">
	<div class="sticky">
		<div class="logo">
			<%= link_to root_path do %>
				<%= image_tag "lookin-logo.png" %>
			<% end %>
		</div>

		<div class="user">
			<% if current_user %>
			<%= link_to 'Sign out', destroy_user_session_path, method: :delete %>
			<% else %>
			<%= link_to 'Sign up', new_user_registration_path, :class => "button" %>

			<%= link_to 'Sign in', new_user_session_path, :class => "button" %>
			<% end %>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="parentabout">
		<p align="center" class="bg-purple"><%= image_tag "girl-meditating.svg" %></p>
		<h2>About Us</h2>
		<p>'LOOKIN' meditation app has born with the idea to help people to get engaged in a meditative state of mind helping relieve stress and anxiety caused by our routine activities and overthinking.<br><br>The application is very simple to use, you just have to download on your phone, sign up and start enjoying the 30 days trial.<br><br>The audios available on the app are all guided meditations and are divided into 4 categories: inner peace, love, confidence, and yin-yang. The recorded length takes about 5 to 30 minutes and there is an option to download if you'd like to listen to them on a flight mode for example.<br><br>As much more you practice meditation, the better you become, therefore, we suggest you take the advantage of the favorites feature to access your most liked meditations anywhere, anytime.<br><br>Enjoy your time meditating with us and always remember to 'look in' yourself.<br><br>Namaste!<br><br>Lookin Team</p>
	</div>

	<div class="footerWrap">
    <div class="footer">
      <div class="footerContent">
      	<hr><br>
        <p>2019 All the rights reserved to Lookin Meditation</p>
      </div>     
    </div>
	</div>

</div>

